CustomField.description: Defines the number of days prior to the current date to calculate real time utilization data. Set to 0 to start calculation from the current date. The default value is 50.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Defines the number of days prior to the current date to calculate real time utilization data. Set to 0 to start calculation from the current date. The default value is 50.
